To provide in-app notifications for significant updates on user requests, we need to:

1. Implement a notification service.
2. Extend the WebSocket logic to push in-app notifications to the user when significant events occur.
3. Create front-end logic to display these notifications.

Epic Title: Real-time Status Updates and Notifications

We will:
1. Create a model for notifications.
2. Implement a service for managing notifications.
3. Extend the status update logic to add notifications.
4. Create front-end components to display notifications.

